{"tid":227641,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港民族黨【請即罷考BCA】","createTime":"2017-05-03T10:25:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-04T07:55:10.000Z","uid":28366,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"17d4dac97be680027426d9f0c9146f420cc9a3ca","tid":227641,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T10:25:19.000Z","msg":"【請即罷考BCA】<br />\n殖民政府無視家長合理訴求，基本能力評估研究計劃（BCA，前稱TSA）開考在即，繼續令眾多港人子女受到不必要的精神壓力，試圖使更多年輕人走上絕路。為逼令殖民政府今後撤銷評估，敝黨謹以以下短片向各位揭示政權壓逼港人子女的事實，並呼籲家長為其子女通知學校拒絕應考BCA，切勿向政權妥協，以免我們的下一代再受傷害。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hknationalparty/videos/645409932324631/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhknationalparty%2Fvideos%2F645409932324631%2F&d=ltJnWG3kir489%2BLnRwft2%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=52ffc4dc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hknationalparty/videos/645409932324631/</a>"},{"pid":"99186dea839029e0a702af485dd7be62a2e3cf33","tid":227641,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T10:25:34.000Z","msg":"Pro<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a56dab79005dd84a932396f7c9eaa420f640c45d","tid":227641,"uid":64966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T10:26:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dbace85f5a27ddb2b5ea1898f87cc2cb3350b60","tid":227641,"uid":60607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T10:39:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/f